102
00:04:30.588 --> 00:04:32.757
Didn't anyone tell ya?

103
00:04:32.840 --> 00:04:35.885
There's no way to change
a story once it's been told.

104
00:04:38.638 --> 00:04:40.014
[sighs]

105
00:04:46.520 --> 00:04:47.813
